267
00:14:48,208 --> 00:14:50,375
You eat, sleep, and breathe
this military stuff, don't you?

268
00:14:50,458 --> 00:14:52,583
No, I don't think I'd
put it quite like that.

269
00:14:52,666 --> 00:14:55,333
Did you know that I got photos
