278
00:15:13,333 --> 00:15:15,375
[KURZ laughs]

279
00:15:16,791 --> 00:15:18,291
[SOUSUKE]
No, I think it's 11.

280
00:15:18,375 --> 00:15:20,208
[SHINJI]
Is it? Well, in any case,

281
00:15:20,291 --> 00:15:23,166
