284
00:15:29,208 --> 00:15:32,166
[SOUSUKE]
I see... You may be right.

285
00:15:32,250 --> 00:15:34,833
Would you say, then, that it's
best suited for ambush tactics?

286
00:15:34,916 --> 00:15:37,083
[SHINJI] Yeah, and it's
gonna be a long time...

287
00:15:37,166 --> 00:15:38,541
They're having a nice chat.

288
00:15:38,625 --> 00:15:42,833
Could this be the beginning
