357
00:18:45,458 --> 00:18:49,375
Your tour of duty as Kaname
Chidori's bodyguards... is over.

358
00:18:49,458 --> 00:18:50,500
Uh-- huh?

359
00:18:50,583 --> 00:18:51,916
I don't understand.

360
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,916
It says here that they
were able to destroy

361
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:55,458
the enemy's main facility.

362
00:18:55,541 --> 00:18:57,458
