along with Miss Chidori anymore.

364
00:19:00,625 --> 00:19:02,416
Aw, man. Happens all the time.

365
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:04,708
You get to know somebody,
and then they're gone.

366
00:19:04,791 --> 00:19:08,041
It was such a
short-lived romance.

367
00:19:08,125 --> 00:19:11,083
Wait, it also says we get
a week off here in Tokyo!

368
00:19:11,166 --> 00:19:13,083
You're kidding! That rocks!

369
00:19:13,166 --> 00:19:15,666
[MELISSA] However, Urzu 7 is
to attend the school trip,

370
00:19:15,750 --> 00:19:16,958
as was previously planned.

371
00:19:17,041 --> 00:19:17,833
